parameters:
Oh, you dropped it in a place like this! I'm glad
I found it~! Thank you very much.

If you have a \C[2]lock-picking tool\C[0] and a
\C[2]hairpin\C[0], you might be able to challenge
unlocking the door...

The loli character with the ability to use Baka
Power skill destroys a rock!

It seems like they can destroy the rock if they
can use it.

They've appeared! The demons that Zack was talking
about!

\C[10]I have demons, I have demons... The scent of
platinum nuggets is wafting...

It seems like they're attacking people who have
this gold dust. But it won't go that way today.

\C[10]Demons\C[0], what I desire is... your hearts
tainted with desire... I am devouring your
shameful forms beautifully...

I see, so they weren't attacking specifically for
this gold dust. Well then, I guess we don't need
it after all.
\C[10]Demon\C[0] Ahh? You... what are you doing...

Konoha dumped all the platinum nuggets she had
collected into the water!

What? So you're saying you actually want the
hearts of people tainted with desire, not this
gold dust? That's laughable.

\C[10]Demon\C[0]... Gold... Gold... My... My
gold... Ahhhhhhhh

About the platinum dust I scattered earlier, it
was a lie. It was just regular sand. It seems like
regular sand looked like gold dust.

If you're easily deceived by me, then aren't you
disqualified as a demon?

Phew... I managed to defeat it. Let's report back
to Zack.
